text: Scott Leo "Taye" Diggs (born January 2, 1971) is an American actor and singer. He acted in Broadway musicals Rent and Hedwig and the Angry Inch. He acted in the movies Equilibrium, How Stella Got Her Groove Back and Brown Sugar. Diggs was born in Newark, New Jersey.
